               <H2>Market Summary</H2>
               <p>Merivale Mall is located on the busiest major artery in Nepean. Built in 1976, it is in the planning stages of major redevelopment. With anchors such as Farm Boy, Sport Chek, Shoppers Drug Mart, YMCA Fitness and a 22,000 square feet sportsbar it has something for everyone. The community shopping centre serves the immediate needs of the surrounding neighbourhood as well as the overall needs of an enlarged trading area due to the unique anchors. Now proudly managed by Bentall Kennedy.</p>
